 * 
 * @fields_start
 * 
 * group:content => 内容设置
 * content.badge => 徽章文字:text:FAQ
 * content.title => 标题:text:Frequently Asked Questions
 * content.description => 描述:textarea:Everything you need to know about playing rummy on RummyRoyal.
 * 
 * group:faq => FAQ列表
 * faq.items => FAQ列表:textarea:Is online rummy legal in India?|Yes, the Supreme Court of India has declared rummy as a game of skill. It is legal to play online rummy for cash in most Indian states.\r\nHow do I withdraw my winnings?|You can withdraw your winnings instantly via UPI, bank transfer, or Paytm. Minimum withdrawal is ₹100 and processing is within minutes.\r\nIs it safe to play on RummyRoyal?|Absolutely. We use RNG-certified card shuffling, SSL encryption for data protection, and are licensed by recognized gaming authorities.\r\nWhat are the entry fees for games?|Entry fees vary by format. Practice tables are free. Cash games start from as low as ₹1 entry fee. Tournament entry ranges from ₹10 to ₹10,000.\r\nHow does the welcome bonus work?|New players get up to ₹5,000 welcome bonus on their first deposit. The bonus is released in installments as you play cash games.\r\nCan I play on my mobile phone?|Yes! Our app is available on Android and iOS. You can also play directly in your mobile browser without downloading.|格式：问题|回答，一行一个
 * 
 * @fields_end
